---
title: Smokey Pork Schnitzel & Cucumber Cos Salad with Avocado & Balsamic Glaze
description: Crispy, crunchy, golden and delicious - what could it be? It’s a juicy pork schnitzel, with our smokey Kiwi spice blend cooked right into the crumb. This showstopper is perfectly paired with a simple cos salad, with creamy avocado and refreshing cucumber. Grab a fork and dig in!
